TopicTitle: Why am I getting an error message for B9PartSwitch ?

Articles.Content: Why do I get a popup during the loading process that reads... "B9PartSwitch - Serious Warning" and below it says "More than one module can't manage a part's crashTolerance" and "Please see KSP's log for additional details" this just started happening yesterday when I tried to load a game. Is anyone else having the same issue?

First, it would be better to post this in the B9 thread where others can see it.

Did you update any mods recently?
